      • writeCnf

        public static void writeCnf(java.lang.String fname,
            boolean out)
        Write a CNF encoding of the given boolean to the named file such that an "unsatisfiable" result indicates that the boolean is always true. When invoked in a standard JVM, does nothing.
        Parameters:
